sc_cat_item.description:
This is an automated self service request, it will require approval from

  • Service or Application Owner
  • Automation Team

 

Prerequisites to submit request:

  • A GIT Project
  • A File based project inventory

The following Ansible Tower objects will be created

  • A Team which can be used to assigning permissions to tower objects you create.
  • A Project for pulling you playbook code from GIT into Tower.
  • A Inventory for running playbooks against.
  • A project based file inventory source for dynamically populating the inventory.

 

Details will be sent to the ticket and emailed to the requester confirming the name of the Tower objects created
sc_cat_item.name: Ansible Tower Onboarding Request
